cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote SCTP data port to a mismatched value prevents proper F1 data interface connection, disrupting user plane traffic.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Altering the remote N address to an incorrect IP prevents F1 network interface communication, causing CU-DU link failure.
